article.headline: Saterfield puts up 10 in Portland State's 62-55 victory against Air Force
article.description: — Jorell Saterfield scored 10 points as Portland State beat Air Force 62-55 in the season-opener for both teams on Monday.
article.linkText: Saterfield puts up 10 in Portland State's 62-55 victory against Air Force
article.story: COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo. -- — Jorell Saterfield scored 10 points as Portland State beat Air Force 62-55 in the season-opener for both teams on Monday. Saterfield also contributed seven rebounds for the Vikings. Kaelen Allen shot 0 of 5 from the field and 8 for 10 from the line to add eight points. Isiah Kirby shot 4 of 5 from the field to finish with eight points. Beau Becker finished with 14 points, seven rebounds and two blocks for the Falcons. Chase Beasley added 14 points and four assists for Air Force. In addition, Ethan Taylor finished with 11 points, five assists and two steals. NEXT UP Portland State's next game is Thursday against UCSB on the road. Air Force visits LIU on Friday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
